support-looks-like-on-a-website/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;What good feed reader (RSS) support looks like on a website&lt;/a&gt;」 &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="emoji"&gt;4️⃣&lt;/span&gt;「&lt;a href="https://amxmln.com/blog/2025/spicing-up-your-feeeeds/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;Spicing up your feeeeds&lt;/a&gt;」&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="emoji"&gt;5️⃣&lt;/span&gt;「&lt;a href="https://blog.mochi.is/p/trigger-actions-on-new-feed-items" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;Trigger actions on new feed items with IFTTT and Feed Control&lt;/a&gt;」&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="emoji"&gt;6️⃣&lt;/span&gt;「&lt;a href="https://rubenerd.com/using-rss-over-json-feeds/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;Using RSS over JSON Feeds?&lt;/a&gt;」&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="emoji"&gt;7️⃣&lt;/span&gt;「&lt;a href="https://openrss.org/blog/using-cloudflare-on-your-website-could-be-blocking-rss-users" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;Using Cloudflare on your website could be blocking RSS users&lt;/a&gt;」&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="emoji"&gt;8️⃣&lt;/span&gt;「&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-5MtaffecZU" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;Switch to RSS for your online media!&lt;/a&gt;」 &lt;a href="https://t.me/aboutrss/1507?q=%23YouTube"&gt;#YouTube&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="emoji"&gt;9️⃣&lt;/span&gt;「&lt;a href="https://hobbies.deimos-legion.net/2025/01/21/rediscovering-rss/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;Rediscovering RSS&lt;/a&gt;」&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="emoji"&gt;🔟&lt;/span&gt;「The Anatomy of an RSS Reader」 Part &lt;a href="https://primatology.xyz/blog/the-anatomy-of-an-rss-reader-part-1" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href="https://primatology.xyz/blog/the-anatomy-of-an-rss-reader-part-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href="https://primatology.xyz/blog/the-anatomy-of-an-rss-reader-part-3" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;上一期：【&lt;a href="https://t.me/aboutrss/1496" target="_blank" rel="noopener" onclick="return confirm('Open this link?\n\n'+this.href);"&gt;68&lt;/a&gt;】&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="https://cdn1.telesco.pe/file/TM9glnNusXRMkBsjS43bCFMQoFdIR5GPYmOmbmNDIwNfWLiJXmmBfvVx66IHcGIrc9JQFEsxTh17ntk7PFe9P453yRp-FYjYf-uCzy2pbvqx59mNr7RxCyzfNEfGTJMexVrpR5QUgmA7263PhgVSLW_jQ3hgwEv9e86sOG5kGaoqyTBwnaxKR0_mAeyLH4eY-JAgCVnSzlndF2G4qSvToYKorcoOAwwcyEsy1jUl5Fd5oeoKV7Pn79yCNbalRnwO2noRKuziv8OBEeX5q9Zm-ENGs5nW9Xsrlcjf3Fm7L4ehqEQ2bfp3VuR4q61FUyXoKtZ20UYEZtQKY2VnFY9liA.jpg" width="640" height="360" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;</description><link>https://t.me/aboutrss/1507</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://t.me/aboutrss/1507</guid><pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 12:04:09 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>🖼 Kindly RSS Reader: 面向 e-ink 设备的需自架 RSS 阅读器</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Kindly RSS Reader: 面向 e-ink 设备的需自架 RSS 阅读器&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;该阅读器 &lt;a href="https://t.me/aboutrss/1506?q=%23%E5%BC%80%E6%BA%90"&gt;#开源&lt;/a&gt; 需要自部署，不挑服务器配置，支持 RSS 和 Atom 源，专为 &lt;a href="https://t.me/aboutrss/1506?q=%23%E7%94%B5%E7%BA%B8%E4%B9%A6"&gt;#电纸书&lt;/a&gt; 设备优化。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://kindlyrss.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://kindlyrss.app/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;发现于作者嘟文：&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://mastodon.social/@nicoan@fosstodon.org/113951953833125673"